Investigar ORM OJO  => Active Record

en el terminal instal

Confiuracion de Ubuntu con Servidor SQL SErver 2008
https://github.com/rails-sqlserver/activerecord-sqlserver-adapter/wiki/Platform-Installation---Ubuntu

sudo apt-get install freetds-dev freetds-bin tdsodbc

https://github.com/rails-sqlserver/activerecord-sqlserver-adapter/wiki/Using-TinyTds

gem install tiny_tds
gem install activerecord-sqlserver-adapter

agregar al gem file

gem 'tiny_tds'
gem 'activerecord-sqlserver-adapter'

bundle install


